Input card have to be created in two rows for ease of input.
1st row is for inputs from TIME to SOx/CO2
2nd row is for inputs from OCL PP A to W. COMP

Close input card in frame with to rows as mentioned above. frame is for separation and beter visibility later

Input card fillup have two requirements
IF Event name piced by user is MID, then all parameters must be filled by user.
ELSE Event name is different than MID, then only first row must be filled and second row is not active and cannot be filled


Logs must be keept in separate file as some sort of database. Pick solution that will be light, easy to modify when tens of tousands or more  of entries will exist.
Values from data base also will be constantly accesible from application to view and modify.

On main screen on the left side there must be panel.
This panel will be called Events loogbok

Panel is for display all existing events that were created by user.
In this panel all entries must be showed in Excel form 
One row is one event entry where every cell is for saved or calculated values (calculations will be explained in instruction_2 that will be created after results will be satysfying)

This panel have to be able to expand .
Expansion have to be done by user. USer click and hold by mouse coursor by side of frame and can dynamicaly shrink or expand panel. 
This will give user good visibility of historical inputs.

Under latest entry please put small NEW ENTRY button that will create empty event for filling up.

When NEW ENTRY button clicked the input card is empty and ready for inputs.
